  "body": "This is low priority!\r\n\r\nTeku version: 21.10.1\r\n\r\nWhile running a fresh sync, Epoch events are output to the console every 6.4 minutes. This looks a bit weird and seems pointless.\r\n\r\nSuggestion: suppress these `Epoch Event` messages while syncing.\r\n\r\n```\r\n17:40:35.030 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370201, Head slot: 1238, Remaining slots: 2368963, Connected peers: 15\r\n17:40:47.039 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370202, Head slot: 1439, Remaining slots: 2368763, Connected peers: 18\r\n17:40:59.093 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370203, Head slot: 1620, Remaining slots: 2368583, Connected peers: 28\r\n17:41:11.023 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370204, Head slot: 2250, Remaining slots: 2367954, Connected peers: 24\r\n17:41:23.030 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370205, Head slot: 2945, Remaining slots: 2367260, Connected peers: 23\r\n17:41:35.065 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370206, Head slot: 3500, Remaining slots: 2366706, Connected peers: 24\r\n17:41:47.023 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370207, Head slot: 4150, Remaining slots: 2366057, Connected peers: 27\r\n17:41:47.513 INFO  - Epoch Event *** Epoch: 74069, Justified checkpoint: 128, Finalized checkpoint: 127, Finalized root: 73fd33..0068\r\n17:41:59.139 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370208, Head slot: 4928, Remaining slots: 2365280, Connected peers: 30\r\n17:42:11.025 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370209, Head slot: 6041, Remaining slots: 2364168, Connected peers: 29\r\n17:42:23.024 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370210, Head slot: 6550, Remaining slots: 2363660, Connected peers: 28\r\n17:42:35.084 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370211, Head slot: 7247, Remaining slots: 2362964, Connected peers: 33\r\n17:42:47.024 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370212, Head slot: 7750, Remaining slots: 2362462, Connected peers: 30\r\n17:42:59.024 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370213, Head slot: 8300, Remaining slots: 2361913, Connected peers: 29\r\n17:43:11.024 INFO  - Syncing     *** Target slot: 2370214, Head slot: 8900, Remaining slots: 2361314, Connected peers: 27\r\n```\r\n\r\nRunning the leveldb-tree sync in this case - don't know if it is unique to this or not.",
